20:50.453 --> 20:52.967
You know what, you ain't got to do
nothing, Uncle Phil.

20:53.133 --> 20:54.885
It ain't like I'm still 5 years old.

20:55.093 --> 20:57.653
Ain't like I'll be sitting up
every night asking my mom:

20:57.813 --> 20:59.963
"When's Daddy coming home?"
Who needs him?

21:00.173 --> 21:03.529
He wasn't there to teach me how
to shoot my first basket, but I learned.

21:03.693 --> 21:05.490
- And I got pretty good at it too.
- Yeah.

21:05.653 --> 21:08.645
Got through my first date without him.
I learned how to drive.

21:08.813 --> 21:10.804
I learned how to shave.
How to fight.

21:10.973 --> 21:13.851
I had 14 great birthdays without him.

21:14.013 --> 21:18.052
He never even sent me a damn card.
To hell with him!

21:23.053 --> 21:25.248
I didn't need him then
and I don't need him now.

21:25.413 --> 21:27.131
- Will...
- You know what, Uncle Phil?

21:27.293 --> 21:29.204
I'm gonna get through college
without him.

21:29.373 --> 21:30.931
I'll get a great job without him.

21:31.133 --> 21:33.647
I'll marry a beautiful honey,
have a bunch of kids...

21:33.813 --> 21:35.769
...and be a better father
than he ever was.

21:35.933 --> 21:38.527
I don't need him for that,
because there ain't a thing...

21:38.733 --> 21:41.611
...he could ever teach me
about how to love my kids.

21:49.093 --> 21:51.687
How come he don't want me, man?

